#TRX_REVIEWS_PLACEHOLDER#
Monday nights we host Yappy Hour on our patio!
Bring your pup and your second drink is on us. We also have free home-made doggy treats.
Also on Mondays inside, join us for Free Texas Hold ‘Em at 7pm.
Tuesdays we offer Game Night with an array of board games
Wednesday is 2-4-1 Irish Draft night, 9pm-midnight
Thursday Car Bombs are $4, 7pm-close
Friday’s we offer $3 Guinness blondes from 11am -7pm
Saturday and Sunday Brunch: $3 Mimosas and Bellini’s and a variety of Bloody Mary’s
</section> class="post_content" itemprop="articleBody">
